name: De aquí y de allá
description:
We are from here and from over there. We are everywhere. We are everything. 

This art was originally exhibited as a part of Wish You Were Here: 17th Annual Postcard Show at A.I.R. Gallery in New York City, New York which took place from 24 May 2018 - 24 Jun 2018. Curated by Judith Tolnick Champa. 

Single edition by Edgar Fabián Frías / @edgarfabianfrias | 1800 x 1200 | .jpg | 2018.
